{"tid":2263794,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個最近覺得自己好仆街嘅一件事","createTime":"2020-10-30T07:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T18:00:58.000Z","uid":20032,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5915a067a939b7933c3f002f842a08347ee5c525","tid":2263794,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"新鮮滾熱辣<br />\n事先聲明，我係大家口中嘅道德撚<br />\n下面發生嘅事係令我好內疚同羞愧，但我真係好想share俾大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪有啲婆婆烏低身烏到好低，腰唔好嘅<br />\n<br />\n我頭先低住頭㩒手機入長沙灣嗰啲小巷打算行快啲<br />\n<br />\n一轉彎，突然有個烏到勁低嘅啊婆出現係我眼前<br />\n<br />\n我剎那間以為係到我腰咁高嘅大黑狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我膝頭即刻軟一軟，再企返直咁<br />\n<br />\n好似半踎再即刻起身咁，嚇餐死，嗰下真係好驚"},{"pid":"f5f6f723620c035bc6b033b91a6f8155d8e7908f","tid":2263794,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"入嚟睇依個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68434cffe1abf242da6312f892e5076eecc2f6a0","tid":2263794,"uid":127425,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"唔明有幾仆街"},{"pid":"acf6d3027bc5c762a509098e8a909c91468991d6","tid":2263794,"uid":375919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"上連登"},{"pid":"c361c89f991b274558503871ef873928b56f5b56","tid":2263794,"uid":358542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:05:05.000Z","msg":"不如話見到你老友大蕃薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318cf6ca5db8f629e9662c0289029d0bb51346ae","tid":2263794,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:06:44.000Z","msg":"琴日喺街上面偷偷放左個屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a548e05bcdb364340a593e0ad432c4015446d44","tid":2263794,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"68434cffe1abf242da6312f892e5076eecc